"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"![Image courtesy Firmbee.com and edited by Writer's Career. In the image, it says: content production for the web. Expression in Brazilian Portuguese.](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/iFmXm2vZNBbrEUu1IMuMP.png?height=512&width=1024)\\n\\nYeah, writers! In this post, we will know the story of a farmer who works with content marketing in the 19th century. The tour guide that today gives stars to great chefs. The brand's magazine and when and where the term Content Marketing appeared and what is its importance for your brand as a writer, that and more, follow me until the end of the reading.\\n\\n## How Content Production Came: The Agricultural Magazine “The Furrow”\\n\\n![Google image](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/-DRszTeOZ0i4D_I-Zn_6Q.png?height=168&width=300)\\n\\nInserting content into a marketing strategy, or at least something like it, which we call content marketing, came from John Deere, owner of an agricultural machinery company of the same name. He launched the company's own publication in 1895 called “The Furrow”.\\n\\n![Google Image](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/5p-PDbIWmGfUJoBtJOq_a.png?height=1024&width=683)\\n\\nJohn did not use the magazine to advertise his agricultural vehicles, rather the farmer used it to bring information to the target audience, production techniques, market news and “success stories” from consumers of his product.\\n\\n## Michelin Gastronomy and Tourism Guide, Michelin Gastronomy and Tourism Guide.\\n\\n![Google image](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/lHz7FcTyRrG1OFrOgs6qw.png?height=183&width=275)\\n\\nThe Michelin Guide to gastronomy and tourism was far more effective than any sales catalog. At the beginning of the 20th century, the first copies of the “Michelin Guide” by the famous French tire manufacturer began to circulate. So that people would have reasons to hit the road and travel with their private car (consequently to buy more tires).\\n\\n![Google Image](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/orHdoHJ9qNoiN1sXkMQQG.png?height=135&width=372)\\n\\n# Lego\\n\\n![Image courtesy of Xavi Cabrera](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/b8zn4tN6pD_DvQxBk0Ves.png?height=682&width=1024)\\n\\nDuring the last century, Lego along with other companies, explored the production of content marketing, in 1980 it published its own magazine “Brick Kicks”. The magazine demonstrates that its toys went beyond entertainment, used for educational purposes.\\n\\n![Google image](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/iBT4cM6X2WJzT1oHb_bSI.png?height=258&width=195)\\n\\n## The editorial house of the big brands.\\n\\n![Image courtesy of Merakist](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/6Q144KrhJCVbCze2Ez8o4.png?height=525&width=700)\\n\\nCustom Publishing Council, in the United States, created in 1998. A company that published magazines exclusively for brands having a great success. The emergence of the Term And finally, in 2001, Penton Custom Media coined the term content marketing. The American company was led by Joe Pulizzi founder of the (CMI) Content Marketing Institute.\\n\\n##  Understanding the importance of content production to your success.\\n\\n\\n[Also read: What is copywriting and what makes a copywriter, create a good copy.](http://carreiradeescritor.com/2021/09/06/o-que-e-copywriting-e-o-que-faz-um-copywriter-fazer-uma-boa-copy/)\\n\\n![Image courtesy of Kaleidico](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/C3yZpg78benvUC3EW5ldL.png?height=466&width=700)\\n\\nThe main connection channel between you, your offer and your potential consumer is content. It is through the content that your message reaches the persona of your business with your mission, vision and values. Of course, because this brings closeness and relationship, without a shadow of a doubt it is a trade-off. The consumer wants relevant content, he wants to buy a product, and will do so when he consumes enough content about a certain subject.\\n\\nHowever, content production does not break all barriers, so here comes the Digital Marketing strategies.\\n\\nWith an aligned strategy and content, the product almost takes on a life of its own and begins to speak for itself.\\n\\nHere are some advantages:\\n\\n* Increases engagement between customers and the brand, contributing to increased sales and revenue.\\n\\n\\n* \\n  The conversion rate, which demonstrates the number of visitors that turn into 'leads', or potential customers, increases as trust is aroused through the content;\\n  the more relevant content there is, the greater the interest and browsing time of users;\\n* \\n  As brands produce content, their importance in search engines increases in relevance. That means being among the top search pages;\\n* \\n  the company's reach and visibility on social media also increases due to the sharing of relevant content;\\n\\nWe've seen the rise of content marketing in history and its importance. As a writer, blogger or entrepreneur, you must be aware of what was said and try to apply content production to your brand/company if you want to succeed in the digital realm.\\n\\nYeah, writers! We've come to the end of another post on the Writer's Career blog, and I hope I have clarified it in some way about Content Production for the Web. For more tips and content, follow the blog, let your liking help me a lot!\",\"timestamp\":1641081127,\"title\":\"How did content marketing come about and what is its importance for my brand as a writer.\"},\"digest\":\"nZLy04_XuUwMAUST_caPgKaYy4G2KPZwGRm0dHGpXT4\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xab210e2600C72E26f0e38D43D71a551aA8494EC4\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"28TVK4Ftv7y9cR8GIyyYBmhx1-0EgGjVp0Kzx9iu3o8\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"QEO0JhnQchvctiQKaACG_rp6JPS9Gm6_n4oA60OogGA\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"-q7snHPBHqgk